    <title type="html"><![CDATA[TextMate and RVM Gemset]]></title>
    <link href="http://plum.iodot.org/blog/2011/11/10/textmate-and-rvm-gemset/"/>
    <updated>2011-11-10T10:41:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://plum.iodot.org/blog/2011/11/10/textmate-and-rvm-gemset</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Navigate to <code>Preferences</code> -> <code>Advanced</code> -> <code>Shell Variables</code>, add followed variables:</p>

<p><div><script src='https://gist.github.com/1365809.js?file='></script>
<noscript><pre><code>TM_RUBY: /Users/Jun/.rvm/bin/rvm-auto-ruby
GEM_HOME: env | grep GEM_HOME | awk '{ sub(/GEM_HOME=/, &quot;&quot;); print }'
GEM_PATH: env | grep GEM_PATH | awk '{ sub(/GEM_PATH=/, &quot;&quot;); print }'</code></pre></noscript></div>
</p>
]]></content>
